        <p class="mb-4">
          If you're a cryptographer, election official, policy wonk, or just someone who's tired of
          hearing "the system is broken" with no one offering a blueprint — read it, tear it apart,
          and make it better.
        </p>

        <p class="font-bold text-xl">That's the point.</p>
